   "source": [
    "# Lematizar los tokens -> palabras a su forma base ejemplo running a run\n",
    "lemmatizer = WordNetLemmatizer()\n",
    "lemmatized_tokens = [lemmatizer.lemmatize(token) for token in cleaned_tokens]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Mostrar los primeros 10 ejemplos de palabras originales y lematizadas\n",
    "for original, lemmatized in zip(cleaned_tokens[:250], lemmatized_tokens[:250]):\n",
    "    if(original != lemmatized):\n",
    "        print(f\"Original: {original}, Lematizada: {lemmatized}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Contar la frecuencia de las palabras lematizadas\n",
    "word_freq = Counter(lemmatized_tokens)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Obtener las 10 palabras m√°s comunes\n",
    "most_common_words = word_freq.most_common(40)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Separar las palabras y sus frecuencias para la gr√°fica\n",
    "words, frequencies = zip(*most_common_words)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Graficamos\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "plt.plot(words, frequencies, marker='o', linestyle='-', color='blue')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Palabras')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Frecuencia')\n",
    "plt.title('Top n palabras lematizadas m√°s comunes en firefox.txt')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]

    "# Ejemplo: realizar una desmabiguaci√≥n semantica para bank. Recordar que bank puede tener diferentes significados (ver signficado)\n",
    "example = \"He went to the bank to withdraw some money.\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# Tokenizamos la frase\n",
    "tokens = nltk.word_tokenize(example)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Obtener los posibles Synsets para la palabra 'bank'\n",
    "possible_synsets = wn.synsets('bank')\n",
    "print(possible_synsets)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Mostramos los Synsets disponibles para 'bank'\n",
    "print(\"Possible synsets for 'bank':\")\n",
    "for synset in possible_synsets:\n",
    "    print(f\"{synset.name()}: {synset.definition()}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Desambiguaci√≥n basada en contexto\n",
    "# Buscamos la definici√≥n que nos permita entender el ejemplo de la frase\n",
    "context_synset = None\n",
    "for synset in possible_synsets:\n",
    "    if 'money' in synset.definition() or 'financial' in synset.definition():\n",
    "        context_synset = synset\n",
    "        break\n",
    "print(\"\\n\")\n",
    "# Mostramos el Synset seleccionado como el m√°s probable, y que nos permite la desmabiguaci√≥n sem√°ntica\n",
    "if context_synset:\n",
    "    print(f\"Synset - Significado m√°s probale seg√∫n el contexto: {context_synset.name()}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"Definition: {context_synset.definition()}\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"\\nNo se encontraron\")"
   ]
